::'''Dolimem:''' The paths to Membrance Maze have long been forgotten. Your arrival has brought the forest back to life!
::'''Dolimem:''' Since the leaves and vines have opened wide to welcome you, since ancient songs have guided your steps &mdash; we too shall treat you as an honored guest. We'll gather 'round the fire and share the rain, the stories, and the laughter.
::'''Dolimem:''' Hehe... when that day comes, don't forget to tell us your story, too.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504115001_10-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504115001_10-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504115001_10-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How did you become a village chief?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504115005-->
:::'''Dolimem:''' Hehe... that was a long time ago. Back then, saplings had yet to stretch toward the sky. You could still count the rings inside a tree stump. And the Maze wasn't nearly as full as it is today.
:::'''Dolimem:''' The first fairies to arrive &mdash; some ran off to play in the deep woods. Some fell asleep and never wanted to wake up. As for me, I simply wandered to wherever help was needed.
:::'''Dolimem:''' I don't know how long it's been. But little by little, the village grew more lively. And then, one day &mdash; hehe... the children just started calling me "Chief."
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} And what does a chief do?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504115009-->
:::'''Dolimem:''' Hehe... being a chief isn't as easy as you think. Planting crops, drawing water &mdash; I have to handle it all. And when the fairies get into fights, I'm the one who has to break them up.
:::'''Dolimem:''' Then there's the praying &mdash; to the heart of Maze. Listening to the whispers of time, interpreting the prophecies it leaves behind.
:::'''Dolimem:''' And above all, there's the waiting. Waiting for the prophecy to come true. Waiting for fate to draw near. Waiting, you see, is the most important job of all.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I'll see you next time.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504115013-->
:::'''Dolimem:''' You have to! It's a promise. When the little ones hear your tales from the outside, they'll wag their tails with joy!
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
