:{{DIcon|Talk}} What's your take on the new restaurant?
::<!--Custom String Listener: choice3-->
::'''Dolimem:''' Hehe... My distinguished guest, oh no, I should call you manager. How's business these days? Still booming?
::'''Dolimem:''' In all my memory, this forest has never been so full of life.
::'''Dolimem:''' I can see the restaurant's plaque from a distance, hear the cheerful noise, and watch fairies who used to drift about aimlessly now find their passion... It's as if the Membrance Maze has finally awakened from a long slumber.
::'''Dolimem:''' I know running a restaurant is no easy feat. Don't push yourself too hard, manager.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I'll see you next time.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504115013-->
